name: Femi's Love: Aisha (A-yeh-sha)
description:
A woman worth ten of her opposite.
They say there had been none like her since the days of the early revolution. Her bloodline was that of submissive celibate home keepers and so her very birth was a shock to all.
But her mother taught her to be valiant. And to understand that she was borne of God's love, flesh and blood.
She grew up incapable of fearing any female. She saw them as lowly and not of her kind.
Her lack of father enabled her to be both child and parent to herself.
Noble. Wise and most obviously,
beautiful.
Her intimidating radiance breathtaking.
Her elegant form always modestly wrapped for none to touch.
Until the day of Femi.
On this day she found her only weakness and she loved him beyond all explanation.
